{"title":"查看你的Misskey存档！","date":"2024-05-28T23:18:59.000Z","source":"_posts/查看你的Misskey存档！.md","raw":"---\ntitle: 查看你的Misskey存档！\ndate: 2024-05-28 23:18:59\ntags:\n  - typescript\n---\n\n简而言之，我写了一个可以查看Misskey/Firefish/Sharkey/...等Misskey系软件导出帖子存档的工具！\n\n网址： https://lhcfl.github.io/misskey-archive-viewer-web\n\n源代码： https://github.com/Lhcfl/misskey-archive-viewer","slug":"查看你的Misskey存档！","published":true,"updated":"2024-07-02T01:56:10.264Z","_id":"cly3rcq5g001dciq84a261g76","comments":true,"layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","html":"<p>简而言之，我写了一个可以查看Misskey/Firefish/Sharkey/…等Misskey系软件导出帖子存档的工具！</p>\n<p>网址： <a href=\"https://lhcfl.github.io/misskey-archive-viewer-web\">https://lhcfl.github.io/misskey-archive-viewer-web</a></p>\n<p>源代码： <a href=\"https://github.com/Lhcfl/misskey-archive-viewer\">https://github.com/Lhcfl/misskey-archive-viewer</a></p>\n","excerpt":"","more":"<p>简而言之，我写了一个可以查看Misskey/Firefish/Sharkey/…等Misskey系软件导出帖子存档的工具！</p>\n<p>网址： <a href=\"https://lhcfl.github.io/misskey-archive-viewer-web\">https://lhcfl.github.io/misskey-archive-viewer-web</a></p>\n<p>源代码： <a href=\"https://github.com/Lhcfl/misskey-archive-viewer\">https://github.com/Lhcfl/misskey-archive-viewer</a></p>\n","path":"2024/05/28/查看你的Misskey存档！/","permalink":"http://lhcfl.github.io/2024/05/28/%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84Misskey%E5%AD%98%E6%A1%A3%EF%BC%81/","tags":[{"name":"typescript","_id":"cly3rcq610042ciq8bjjr6kit","slug":"typescript","path":"tags/typescript/","permalink":"http://lhcfl.github.io/tags/typescript/","length":1}],"categories":[],"prev":{"title":"静态版Ruby？Crystal语言试用","date":"2024-06-13T11:19:28.000Z","slug":"静态版Ruby？Crystal语言试用","published":true,"updated":"2024-07-02T01:56:10.268Z","_id":"cly3rcq5k001mciq8e6q11v4l","layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"<p>前几天在思考，Python和JS都拥抱了类型检查（类型注释），但是Ruby却只能用Sorbet这样的影响性能的类型检查器（Ruby没有官方的类型检查工具，引入静态类型检查的gem反而降低了性能），在搜索中找到了 Crystal 这门语言。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://crystal-lang.org/\">https://crystal-lang.org/</a></p>\n<p>看描述我就惊艳到了：作为一个<strong>静态语言</strong>，Crystal居然长得这么像Ruby，于是本着不妨玩玩的想法，我进行了Crystal的初试。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight crystal\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># A very basic HTTP server</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">require</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;http/server&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">server = <span class=\"symbol\">HTTP:</span>:Server.new <span class=\"keyword\">do</span> |context|</span><br><span class=\"line\">  context.response.content_type = <span class=\"string\">&quot;text/plain&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  context.response.print <span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello world, got <span class=\"subst\">#&#123;context.request.path&#125;</span>!&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">address = server.bind_tcp(<span class=\"number\">8080</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">puts <span class=\"string\">&quot;Listening on http://<span class=\"subst\">#&#123;address&#125;</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># This call blocks until the process is terminated</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">server.listen</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","path":"2024/06/13/静态版Ruby？Crystal语言试用/","permalink":"http://lhcfl.github.io/2024/06/13/%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E7%89%88Ruby%EF%BC%9FCrystal%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E8%AF%95%E7%94%A8/","__post":true},"next":{"title":"node-discourse-api is developing","date":"2023-10-20T10:16:33.000Z","slug":"node-discourse-api","published":true,"updated":"2024-07-02T01:56:10.264Z","_id":"cly3rcq59000yciq8hxn52ccg","layout":"post","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"","path":"2023/10/20/node-discourse-api/","permalink":"http://lhcfl.github.io/2023/10/20/node-discourse-api/","__post":true},"__post":true}